<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ:</span> وَسَأَلْتُ يَحْيَى بْنَ مَعِينٍ عَنِ الْإِيمَانِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> فَقَالَ:</span> الْإِيمَانُ قَوْلٌ وَعَمَلٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قُلْتُ:</span> يَزِيدُ وَيَنْقُصُ؟<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> يَزِيدُ وَيَنْقُصُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>